### TransitOS REST API — примеры (REST Client / VS Code)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Login dispatcher
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "dispatcher",
  "password": "disp123"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ООО Пример",
  "phone": "+74950001122",
  "debtLimit": 50000
}

### List vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List tariffs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Preview price
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/preview-price
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tariffId": "REPLACE_TARIFF_ID",
  "distanceKm": 12,
  "idleHours": 0.5,
  "urgent": false
}

### List orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schedule today
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Login admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Driver rating (admin token required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/drivers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Audit (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
